OPTIFIT APPROACH

1.DISCOVERY MEETING

2.PERFORMANCE ASSESSMENT

3.PROGRAM DESIGN

4.NUTRITION COACHING

5.PROGRESS TRACKING

6.REVIEW, ADAPT & IMPROVE

Our approach follows a scientific-backed model from the National Academy of Sports Medicine. It allows everyone to follow an evidence-based integrated program built with your goal in mind, regardless if you are a high-performing athlete, or someone starting out in their fitness journey. Alongside that, you will be supported by our coaching practice and we will make sure together that you will stay on track and make sure you get results.
BOOK YOUR INTAKE SESSION

MEET THE TRAINER

NASM CPT ANDREI TRANDAFIR

NASM CPT & NUTRITION COACH INTERNATIONAL LICENSEE

MSC. ORGANIZATIONAL PSYCHOLOGY

ACTIVE IN FOOTBALL, TENNIS, MARTIAL ARTS AND ENDURANCE SPORTS

NASM Certified Personal Trainer and Nutrition Coach, Andrei has a background in Organisational Psychology with extensive practice in amateur, as well as professional competitions in sports such as football, tennis and martial arts.
His focus is on developing a well-rounded, balanced and strong body-mind connection that supports your overall well-being. Some of the training tools in his repertoire that will help you reach your goals include resistance training, speed-agility-quickness training, plyo-metric (reactive) training, balance & core strengthening exercises, as well as a holistic approach to nutrition.
